                                            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "has support skill" .


###  http://w3id.org/digiOntoG4hasType
<http://w3id.org/digiOntoG4hasType> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                    rdfs:domain <http://w3id.org/digiOntoG4Digimon> ;
                                    rdfs:range <http://w3id.org/digiOntoG4Type> ;
